Text: "Scream and shout"-- well at least she's honest about it!
She ROCKED the shit out of this one. Thanks for this roucher!

As long time Britney fan, I can say that this is not even close to her best work. Her accent is tragic, and Britney can do so, so much better without this robotic bullshit. She needs to get off that shitty X-factor show and go back into the studio, and make music that her fans can actually dance to. This song is okay, but I would not buy it...
